ActChemical Weapons Convention Implementation Act
PrecisEnactment of the SCHEDULE 1 CHEMICALS REGULATIONS (CHEMICAL WEAPONS CONVENTION) which, inter alia, set out rules as to the national limit of chemicals that can be held in Canada, the conditions governing licence applications and the obligations of licence holders.
